    "Notably, the Smart Agent (SA) program, leveraging the potential of BCT, ensures the protection of patients' privacy during data outsourcing, marking a distinctive feature of the proposed model.",
    "The framework's empirical validation through a meticulous evaluation, including security, ease of use, and user satisfaction, along with a real-world case study, further demonstrates its unique and impactful contribution to advancing the security paradigm in modern eHealth landscapes.",
